1. Connect local MySQL by Sequel Pro

2. Click "Choose Database..." -> Add database

3. Name your database -> "wpc_db", and select encoding: UTF-8 Unicode (utf8) -> Add

4. Click "Query" -> copy & paste below command

CREATE TABLE `blogposts` (
  `id` int unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `title` varchar(512) DEFAULT NULL,
  `desc` text,
  `image_url` varchar(1024) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

, and then click "run..."




